	(tc_gen_reloc): generate relocations for 'BFD_RELOC_MICROBLAZE_64_TEXTPCREL' , 'BFD_RELOC_MICROBLAZE_64_TEXTPCREL'
	Add new linker options for static linking: adjust-insn-abs-refs, disable-multiple-abs-defs
